SQL_STMT_U.val: select CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO, CLNT110_NAME1, HUSR_NAME, CLNT208_HGROUP, CREM_TYPE from :1/CREM, :1/CLNT, :1/ADMN, :1/HUSR where CREM_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CREM_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and exists(select * from :1/CODE where CODE_TYPE=301 and CODE_NUMBERN=CREM_TYPE and CODE_LANGUAGE=':2') and HUSR_ID = CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT and CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT = 1 and ADMN_NO = CLNT101_ADMNO and ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N' and ADMN_TESTCLIENTS = 'N' and ADMN_ENDCLIENTS = 'N' and CLNT212_FCI = 0 :3 order by CREM_ADMNO, CREM_CLNTNO, CREM_TYPE for fetch only
select CREM_NOTICE from :1/CREM where CREM_ADMNO = :2 and CREM_CLNTNO = :3 and CREM_TYPE = :4 order by CREM_ADMNO, CREM_CLNTNO, CREM_TYPE for fetch only
